snippet: A female mallard that had lost most of its tongue and half its bill was found near 59th Street was euthanized at an animal hospital.
abstract: Park rangers in New York City's Central Park discover a female duck that had been mauled by an animal, apparently a dog; the mallard, which had lost most of its tongue and half its bill, is euthanized.
lead_paragraph: A female mallard that had lost most of its tongue and half its bill was found near 59th Street was euthanized at an animal hospital.
